x-sap-shortText: API to record employee attendances and overtime for payroll purpose

info.title: Payroll Time Sheet
info.description:
You can use these APIs to record the information about employee attendances, overtime, on-call times, and allowances.

 You can find your company's API server in [List of API Servers in SAP SuccessFactors.](https://help.sap.com/viewer/d599f15995d348a1b45ba5603e2aba9b/LATEST/en-US/af2b8d5437494b12be88fe374eba75b6.html)
